=====
Star delim
=====
\verb*foo*f% <- delim is 'f'
\verb**foo*f% <- delim is '*'
-----
(program
  (verbatim (verb_command) (star) (verb_body)) (comment)
  (verbatim (verb_command) (star) (verb_body)) (text) (comment))
